headline: 3 Top Fertilizer Stocks to Watch From a Promising Industry
summary: Favorable demand in major markets and improved fertilizer prices should enable the Zacks Fertilizers industry to thrive. NTR, CF and IPI should benefit from supportive industry fundamentals.
